<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>BA Compliance Attestation — {{ presenter_brand }}</title>
<style>
@page {
    size: Letter;
    margin: 0.75in;
    @bottom-center {
        content: "Issued by {{ presenter_brand }}.  Verify: {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}.  Valid until {{ valid_until_human }}.";
        font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
        font-size: 9pt;
        color: #666;
    }
}
body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    color: #222;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-size: 11pt;
}
.letterhead {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #14A89E;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.letterhead h1 {
    font-size: 24pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}
.letterhead .partner-name {
    font-size: 16pt;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
}
.letterhead .period {
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0;
}
.statement {
    margin: 22px 0;
    font-size: 11.5pt;
    line-height: 1.6;
}
.summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 18px 0;
}
.summary-cell {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #f7fafc;
    border-left: 3px solid #14A89E;
}
.summary-cell .num {
    font-size: 22pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 0;
}
.summary-cell .label {
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 2px 0 0 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.section-h {
    font-size: 13pt;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 22px 0 8px 0;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}
table.roster {
    width: 100.000%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 10pt;
}
table.roster th, table.roster td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    vertical-align: top;
}
table.roster th {
    background: #edf2f7;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
}
table.roster .num {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
}
.subcontractor-block {
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #f0f9ff;
    border-left: 3px solid #0284c7;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.disclaimer {
    margin-top: 22px;
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #718096;
    line-height: 1.4;
}
.disclaimer p { margin: 0 0 6px 0; }
.empty-note {
    color: #718096;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 8px 0;
}
.attestation-block {
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #f7fafc;
    border-left: 3px solid #14A89E;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #4a5568;
}
.attestation-block .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.attestation-block .hash {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 9pt;
    word-break: break-all;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="letterhead">
    <h1>BA Compliance Attestation</h1>
    <p class="partner-name">{{ presenter_brand }}</p>
    <p class="period">Issued {{ issued_at_human }} · Valid until {{ valid_until_human }}</p>
</div>

<div class="statement">
    <p>
        <strong>{{ presenter_brand }}</strong> is a Business Associate to the covered entities listed below under executed Business Associate Agreements (45 CFR §164.504(e)). {{ presenter_brand }} performs technical services on the OsirisCare compliance substrate as a Subcontractor under the OsirisCare→{{ presenter_brand }} Subcontractor BAA dated {{ subcontractor_baa_dated_at_human }}. Each downstream BAA below is recorded in {{ presenter_brand }}'s roster and referenced here for {{ presenter_brand }}'s own §164.504(e)(2)(ii) record of the chain.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="summary-grid">
    <div class="summary-cell">
        <p class="num">{{ roster_count }}</p>
        <p class="label">Active downstream BAAs</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-cell">
        <p class="num">{{ onboarded_counterparty_count }}</p>
        <p class="label">On OsirisCare substrate</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-cell">
        <p class="num">{{ total_monitored_sites }}</p>
        <p class="label">Monitored sites</p>
    </div>
</div>

<h2 class="section-h">Downstream BAA Roster</h2>

{% if roster %}
<table class="roster">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Counterparty</th>
            <th>Executed</th>
            <th>Expiry</th>
            <th class="num">Monitored sites</th>
            <th>Signer</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        {% for r in roster %}
        <tr>
            <td>{{ r.counterparty_label }}{% if not r.is_osiris_onboarded %} <em>(non-OsirisCare)</em>{% endif %}</td>
            <td>{{ r.executed_at_human }}</td>
            <td>{{ r.expiry_at_human }}</td>
            <td class="num">{{ r.monitored_site_count if r.is_osiris_onboarded else '—' }}</td>
            <td>{{ r.signer_name }}, {{ r.signer_title }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>
{% else %}
<p class="empty-note">No downstream BAAs recorded yet. Add per-clinic BAAs to {{ presenter_brand }}'s roster from the partner portal.</p>
{% endif %}

<div class="subcontractor-block">
    <strong>Subcontractor BAA (upstream):</strong>
    OsirisCare→{{ presenter_brand }}, dated {{ subcontractor_baa_dated_at_human }}. The substrate operates as a Subcontractor to {{ presenter_brand }}; technical safeguard monitoring evidence (Ed25519-signed, hash-chained, OpenTimestamps-anchored) is preserved in OsirisCare's substrate evidence chain and is independently verifiable per the published check catalog and verify.sh distribution.
</div>

<div class="attestation-block">
    <p><span class="label">Issued by:</span> {{ presenter_brand }}{{ presenter_contact_line }}</p>
    <p><span class="label">Substrate:</span> OsirisCare</p>
    <p><span class="label">Issuance:</span> {{ issued_at_human }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <span class="label">Valid until:</span> {{ valid_until_human }}</p>
    <p><span class="label">Attestation hash:</span> <span class="hash">{{ attestation_hash }}</span></p>
    <p><span class="label">Verify:</span> {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}/{{ attestation_hash[:32] }}</p>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">
    <p>This attestation is {{ presenter_brand }}'s own §164.504(e)(2)(ii) record of its downstream BAA chain. It is audit-supportive evidence; it is not a HIPAA §164.528 disclosure accounting and does not constitute a legal opinion. The roster reflects active downstream BAAs at issuance; verification by hash binds to the snapshot at that time.</p>
    <p>To report a concern, contact compliance@osiriscare.com (best-effort acknowledgment within 7 business days; substantive response within 30 days) or the HHS Office for Civil Rights at hhs.gov/ocr/complaints.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
